  <body>
    <segment id="1">
Lifeblood flourishes
</segment>
    <segment id="12" parent="15" relname="concession">

As is well known, Luckenwalde can use the millions from the urban project to create a practical and modern urban redevelopment in the next few years.
</segment>
    <segment id="2" parent="15" relname="span"> 

But that would be of little use
</segment>
    <segment id="13" parent="2" relname="condition"> 

if, as is currently the case, the B 101 would still be winding through the city in a few years.
</segment>
    <segment id="3" parent="16" relname="span">  


So it can only be a good thing
</segment>
    <segment id="14" parent="3" relname="condition"> 

if the bypass is completed as quickly as possible.
</segment>
    <segment id="4" parent="19" relname="span">

On the way there, an important milestone was laid yesterday with the ceremonial laying of the foundation stone for the construction work on the bypass.
</segment>
    <segment id="5" parent="24" relname="circumstance">  

Everything should be finished in about two years.
</segment>
    <segment id="6" parent="24" relname="list">  

Then the new B 101 will not only provide a fast connection to the highway as the lifeline of the region.
</segment>
    <segment id="7" parent="21" relname="list">  

The bypass guarantees that more peace and quiet will come to the city, 
</segment>
    <segment id="20" parent="21" relname="list"> 

Luckenwalde is becoming more and more attractive as a place to live
</segment>
    <segment id="8" parent="22" relname="interpretation">


But calm is by no means the order of the day in the economic sector
</segment>
    <segment id="9" parent="22" relname="span">  

The new road is intended to attract investors
</segment>
    <segment id="10" parent="9" relname="reason">  


Modern transportation infrastructure is also to be understood as a signal to the economy to settle here or there.
</segment>
    <segment id="11" parent="22" relname="interpretation"> 

What is particularly important is to make it convincingly clear to investors why Luckenwalde can be a worthwhile location for them.

</segment>
<group id="15" type="span" parent="17" relname="span" />
